Installation Instructions:
wget https://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/cudnn/9.15.0/local_installers/cudnn-local-repo-ubuntu2404-9.15.0_1.0-1_amd64.deb
sudo dpkg -i cudnn-local-repo-ubuntu2404-9.15.0_1.0-1_amd64.deb
sudo cp /var/cudnn-local-repo-ubuntu2404-9.15.0/cudnn-*-keyring.gpg /usr/share/keyrings/
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get -y install cudnn  #### no 
####
To install for CUDA 12, perform the above configuration but install the CUDA 12 specific package:
sudo apt-get -y install cudnn9-cuda-12



